{"tid":2262637,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"16歲男生被指去年柴灣襲警 今被裁定罪成 還押候判","createTime":"2020-10-29T09:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T17:07:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2992c6c5fb0b7a3bffac126c125c00303b8ce388","tid":2262637,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10788&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=755f0dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10788</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#崔美霞裁判官<br />\n#1103柴灣 #裁決<br />\n<br />\n鄭(16) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n襲擊警務人員      <br />\n<br />\n速報~<br />\n1v1無其他警員見到，法庭信納控方第一證人，裁定被告罪成。❗️<br />\n<br />\n還押等候索取教導所、勞教中心、更生中心報告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方一度在退庭後要求就被健康理由(上星期做完手術) 申請保釋候判，惟裁判官因辯方沒有準備醫生紙而拒絕。"},{"pid":"c9b206581c4f4803f5beb32ea67c8436fdc7d996","tid":2262637,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"過左氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664c58ddf059b66747b21100a813ac5fee5db2ba","tid":2262637,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:10:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4e7e70913d2c2960590480ef04b15146c0b0063","tid":2262637,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99802f864630b8a20288fc97f06c282f17f24fb3","tid":2262637,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"選擇信隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d890918b25a5c9d78b02b777fdcab80db6e5ff","tid":2262637,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1359ce05a9efd837bf606f3d5bc94a0f33016c2","tid":2262637,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1016dde1cc246b863dcb42389e56847357566997","tid":2262637,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3be3e6d5f175beb01976736752329439168124d","tid":2262637,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"16歲少年涉在去年七區示威中，在柴灣被追捕時兩度推開警員，令他失平衡跌倒拗傷，案件早前審結。崔美霞裁判官今裁決指本案是宗「一對一」的案件，而<span class=\"red\">警員作供並無不合理或不可靠之處，對其證供予以採納</span>，裁定少年襲警罪成，還柙至下月12日判刑，以待索取教導所、勞教中心及更生中心報告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方審訊時質疑，涉案警員曾偉強部份證供是在庭上才首次提及，沒有紀錄在書面證供中，並質疑他求醫時誇大受傷經過。惟崔官今裁決指，曾的書面證供主要紀錄其遇襲經過，其他細節沒仔細描述並無不合理，亦不影響其可靠性。另外，警員的醫療報告與他供稱的受傷經過亦吻合，故接納曾是誠實可靠證人。<br />\n<br />\n崔官裁定，被告鄭頴駿於去年11月3日，在柴灣怡泰街被警員曾偉強捉住上衣截停時，用雙手推撞其左膊及胸口，令他鬆手失平衡跌倒。"},{"pid":"a9a4ff53f48b1346df3599eb081224c75328a984","tid":2262637,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"又係佢"},{"pid":"2b08d892dbefb345fdd6ca16dc62aa86ebf99a14","tid":2262637,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:26:23.000Z","msg":"警甴打人就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />還拖就N條罪"},{"pid":"e9ea6f7e63f0dd8c98c23b37f850b6d538e978c8","tid":2262637,"uid":110043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T